Package: Ass2Data501
Type: Package
Title: Influence Measures for Linear Models
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Amish Verma
Maintainer: The package maintainer <vermaamis@myvuw.ac.nz>
Description: This package provides functions to calculate influence measures
    such as Cook's Distance, DFFITS, and Hadi's Influence Measure for linear models. 
    It also includes utilities for plotting these measures and identifying influential data points.
